(64, 1, '2020-12-21 16:11:47', '2020-12-21 16:11:47', 'Sau tt nguyn n trung tm chng ti vui mng cho n 02 thnh vin mi v nhng v khch mi n tham quan. y c th ni l mt hiu ng tch cc trong vic thay i t tng \"a ng B, Cha M vo vin dng lo\" ti Vit Nam.\r\n\r\nNgy nay, ngi quan tm n trung tm dng lo khng phi l nhng ngi con, chu hay l cc bn tr m chnh cc ng B, Cha M ca chng ta s l ngi i tm hiu nhng ni c dch v chm sc sc khe ngi cao tui ng tin tng  an tm chn lm ni an dng tui gi cho chnh bn thn mnh.\r\n\r\n02 thnh vin mi ca gia nh HOA SEN NHT BN\r\n\r\nTm trng ca cc c khi vo lu tr ti trung tm rt vui v v chp nhn v gia nh cng nh chnh bn thn cc c  chun b tm l rt r rng v sn sng trc khi ng k vo trung tm. Phn ln l do m cc c mun vo trung tm an dng trc ht l v lo cho sc khe ca bn thn mnh, sau l mun to iu kin cho con, chu c thi gian hc tp v lm vic. Ngoi ra cng c mt s l do khc nh khng mun mnh tr thnh gnh nng i vi gia nh.\r\n\r\nL do n tham quan trung tm ca cc v khch thng l  tm hiu c s vt cht cng nh trang thit b , dch v y t ti trung tm nhm chn cho mnh mt ni tt nht  an dng  tui x chiu.\r\n\r\nKhch mi cng nh cc thnh vin ca trung tm rt quan tm n hot ng YOGA do chnh c A Lin trc tip hng dn.\r\n\r\nBa cm tra cng tt c cc khch mi v thnh vin.\r\n\r\nKhng ch ring ngy hm nay , m l tt c cc ngy trung tm ca chng ti lun lun m ca cho n nhng v khch mun n tham quan, tm hiu trung tm. Nu qu khch c nhu cu tham quan xin lin h vi chng ti qua s in thoi: 0274.2222.079. Chng ti s rt vui nu c c s quan tm ca qu khch.', 'M ca tham quan trung tm ngy 23/08/2018', 'Ngy 04/07/2017, bt u khi cng ci to sa cha CSCSSK Ngi Cao Tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn. D kin hon thnh vo trung tun thng 10/2017. C s chnh thc i vo hot ng vo thng 11/2017.', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'mo-cua-tham-quan-trung-tam-ngay-23-08-2018-2__trashed', '', '', '2021-01-21 15:56:20', '2021-01-21 15:56:20', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/hoasen/?p=64', 0, 'post', '', 0),
