8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"394\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-257 size-large\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/VDL-5-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"394\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ba cm tra cng tt c cc khch mi v thnh vin.</span></p>\r\nKhng ch ring ngy hm nay, m l tt c cc ngy trung tm ca chng ti lun lun m ca cho n nhng v khch mun n tham quan, tm hiu trung tm.\r\n\r\nNu qu khch c nhu cu tham quan xin lin h vi Trung tm Chm sc ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn qua s in thoi: 0274.2222.079. Chng ti s rt vui nu c c s quan tm ca qu khch.', 'Trung tm Hoa Sen Nht Bn m ca tham quan trung tm', 'Sau Tt Nguyn n, ngy 24/3/2018, Trung tm Chm sc ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn vui mng cho n 02 thnh vin mi v nhng v khch mi n tham quan.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '70-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-21 16:09:38', '2021-01-21 16:09:38', '', 70, 'https://g98.com.vn/70-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
