(300, 1, '2021-01-21 16:59:13', '2021-01-21 16:59:13', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-269 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"547\" />\r\nB Ng Th Thanh Hng, i din cng ty TOCONTAP - ch u t - trc tip hng dn cc khch mi tham gia tri nghim th v ny</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-270 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"646\" />\r\nTrn xe, cc khch mi va n sng nh nhng va tu tt hi tn lm quen.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-271 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"687\" />\r\nng 9 gi, khi xe va dng bnh, on iu dng ca Trung tm Hoa Sen Nht Bn  ng ch sn  gip  cc c bc xung xe.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-293 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-4b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1018\" height=\"670\" />\r\nVo n ca, mi ngi c thay dp, ngi ngh ngi v dng tr, bnh trc khi nhn phng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-272 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" />\r\nCho n on khch tham quan, b L Th Thanh Hng - Ch tch Hi ng Qun tr kim Tng Gim c Cty TOCONTAP  chia s v m c to lp m hnh chm sc sc khe v tinh thn dnh cho ngi cao tui theo chun cao cp.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">B ni: \"Hn 30 nm lm vic vi cc i tc Nht, khi c dp thm quan m hnh vin dng lo ti y, ti thy rt r rng nh s chm sc tn tnh v hng dch v tt nht nn ngi cao tui Nht Bn c cuc sng rt tt, khe mnh. Thm ch, c c 102 tui nhng i chn vn cn do dai v theo nh gi ca cc bc s l c c th sng t nht thm 5 nm na. y vy m khi v Vit Nam kho st hu ht cc vin dng lo, ti nhn thy cch chm sc, mi trng sng cha khoa hc. Nhng iu ny  thi thc ti phi lm iu g  cho ngi ln tui  cc c ng, c b c th an tm tn hng cuc sng lc x chiu\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-273 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"668\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-274 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"630\" />T khng gian phng ng n nhng vt dng thng ngy nh khn, ly, bn chi nh rng u c sp xp chm cht, ngay ngn v gn gng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-275 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"615\" />\r\niu dng ca trung tm ang gii thiu v chic ging c bit, c t thit k nh ca cc trung tm dng lo  chu u v Nht Bn. Mi ngi rt thch th v chic ging c th nng ln, h xung ty theo  thch ca ngi s dng).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-276 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"617\" />\r\nAnh Kuragaito Yoshiaki - v qun l ngi Nht ca trung tm, c mi ngi yu mn bi s thn thin, d gn. Mc d cch bit v ngn ng, ting Vit ch \"bp b\" nhng Yoshiaki rt nhn ni, anh nm tay tng ngi v khng ngn ngi qu xung bn cnh  hng dn mi ngi xp giy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-278 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"693\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-279 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"676\" />\r\nThc n ca mi ba n c nghin cu v xy dng da trn tiu chun dinh dng ca B Y t v nhu cu ring ca tng ngi. n c kch thc chic bn n cng c tnh ton  ph hp vi chiu cao ca ngi cao tui.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-280 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1079\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-281 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"713\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-282 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-16.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" />\r\nKhch tham quan rt thch th vi phng tp c trang b cc my tp luyn  nng cao sc khe.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-283 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" />\r\nT ban lnh o cng ty TOCONTAP cho n tng nhn vin ti Trung tm chm sc sc khe ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn u tm nim: \"Mi ngi n y u nh nhng ngi thn trong gia nh. Cc c bc cn c chm sc, nng niu tng ly tng t t tinh thn, th cht n ming n n gic ng\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-284 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-19.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" />\r\nD  sang bn kia dc cuc i, nhng cc c, bc vn nhn nhy v cng tr trung v duyn dng trn nn nhc si ng ca bi ht \"60 nm cuc i\" c h ch li thnh \"em i c bao nhiu, 90 mi nm cuc i...\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-285 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"644\" />\r\nChuyn i ny cc iu dng  y khng ch c hiu thm v tnh cch, cch giao tip vi ngi ln tui m cn c chnh cc bc cao nin dy thm v khiu v. Cn phng nh nhng trn ngp nh sng v ting ci. Tht m m v hnh phc!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-286 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"639\" />\r\nPhn giao lu ca TS.BS Trn Ch Cng din ra lc 8 gi ti vi ch  \"X l cp cu t qu\" nhn c s quan tm ca cc v khch tham gia tri nghim 24 gi  Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-287 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-22.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"665\" />\r\nSau mt gic ng tht su ca ti 6/1, bt u ngy mi, mi ngi cng anh Kuragaito Yoshiaki di chuyn n cng vin gn   tp th dc.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-288 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-23.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-289 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-24.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"662\" />\r\nSau bi tp th dc bui sng mi ngi quay tr li trung tm , ngh ngi ,n sng, v chun b t trang  quay v nh...</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-290 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-26.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"607\" />\r\nKhng ch c chm sc, vui chi, cc v khch mi cn c c qu mang v.  l nhng phn nm m Yoshimoto ti ngon c trng ti cao nguyn Bo Lc, Lm ng; bt rau xanh Nht Bn... Tt c u tt cho sc khe.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-291 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-27.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"709\" />\r\nTrc lc chia tay, c on chp hnh lu nim cng qun l v iu dng ca trung tm.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-292 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-28.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"608\" />\r\n24 gi, qu ngn ngi nhng vn   tt c mi ngi cm nhn c s yu thng. Xe ln bnh, cc iu dng khng qun ci cho, vy tay tm bit n khi xe khut hn.</p>\r\n<strong>24 gi gn b vi Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn ti thnh ph mi Bnh Dng, thi khc chia tay, 19 c ch ai cng c mt cht bi hi, lu luyn khng mun ri i.</strong>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-294 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-29a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"587\" height=\"890\" />\r\nCh mt cu ni Nht d  vng (mt m lm vua) m b Nguyn Th Phc (SN 1947, ng ti Q.Bnh Thnh). B ni:  y mt ngy nh c sng mt cuc i mi. Khi tham gia tp th dc, xp giy ri ht karaoke cng cc bn cao nin, trong pht chc ti thc s qun i tui gi. Hy vng sau khi hon thin, Trung tm Hoa Sen Nht Bn s mang n nhiu tin ch hn na cho ngi cao tui.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-295 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-30a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"587\" height=\"885\" />\r\nC Trn Tuyt Mai (60 tui). Ti rt thch cc mn n ca trung tm. Thc n  c tnh ton k cho sc khe, khng  bng qu i hay qu no. Hn na, khi  y ti khng cn thy c n. Ti c thm bn mi. Mi ngi vui v, chan ha vi nhau. Nht nh, sau chuyn i ny ti s k cho bn b nghe  bit rng trung tm chm sc ngi cao tui hay vin dng lo khng phi l ni t bn nh mi ngi vn ngh. Hy vng, trong tng lai, cc th h tr s suy ngh tch cc hn v vn  a b m vo y  va c chm sc tt li yn tm lm n, kim tin - c Mai chia s.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-296 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-31a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"588\" height=\"879\" />\r\nKhi c hi v k nim vui ti trung tm, c Lu Thanh Lam bi ri v \"c qu nhiu nim vui trong ngy nn khng bit bt u t u\". Sau mt hi suy ngh, c cho bit mi s thch th ca c u  dn v nm m Yoshimoto v bi th dc ca anh Kuragaito Yoshiaki - qun l ngi Nht.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-297 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-32a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"628\" height=\"884\" />\r\nB Hunh Th Tuyt Nga - nguyn Ph ch tch Hi Ph n tnh Qung Ngi l v khch c bit ca chuyn i ny. Trong mi gian phng bc n, mi vt dng b u quan st t m  a ra nh gi, gp  chnh xc. B by t: Tht s ti rt hi lng cc dch v  y. S quan tm, i i nhit tnh chnh l im cng rt ln ca trung tm. Hn na, qua trao i ti thy ngoi dch v di hn, ngi ln tui cng c th ng k chng trnh ngh dng ngn hn nh  1 thng, 1 tun hay 1 ngy u c. Khng g b v thi gian gip mi ngi th gin hn. Nu mt mi, bun phin vi cuc sng hng ngy c th chn tour ngh dng theo nhu cu  tip thm nng lng ri quay tr li thng nht.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-298 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-33a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1015\" height=\"673\" />B Phm Th Huyn Chu v cng n tng vi s vui v, chu o ca anh Kuragaito Yoshiaki. Ngoi ra, thc n ti ngon, tay ngh ch bin ti hoa ca u bp iu dng khin c n ung rt ngon ming. Thm vo , nhng bi tp th dc va sc, cc dng c th thao ph hp vi ngi cao tui  thc s thuyt phc c tri tim ca b. B ho hng ni: Hin ti ang sng mt mnh, sau ny c  kh nng ti chnh, ti nht nh s vo y .</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-299 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-34a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1012\" height=\"663\" />\r\nng  Vn Ba (SN 1952, ng ti Q.1).ng cho rng, i ng t chc tour tham quan trung tm thc s rt thng minh bi nu ch i 1-2 ting ri v th khng hiu c chi tit vic n ung, sinh hot, c s vt cht nh th no, nhn r c mt tt v cha tt  ngy hon thin hn. Nh i 1 ngy nh th ng  tri nghim c rt nhiu th, dch v chm sc ca trung tm u kh tt. S nhit tnh, chu o lm ng cm thy tin tng, yn tm hn. iu lm ng hi lng nht chnh l tinh thn cu th ca ban t chc, khi chn thnh ghi nhn s gp  ca tt c mi ngi bng thi  trn trng v quyt tm sa i.</p>', '24 gi tri nghim ti Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen - Nht Bn', '19 c, ch tui t 60 n 84  c 24 gi tri nghim cuc sng  Trung tm Chm sc ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn ngay ti thnh ph mi Bnh Dng.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '268-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-21 16:59:13', '2021-01-21 16:59:13', '', 268, 'https://g98.com.vn/268-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
