(316, 1, '2018-01-08 17:30:41', '2018-01-08 17:30:41', '<div align=\"justify\">Hiu c ni lo ny, nhn<a href=\"https://alobacsi.com/thoi-su/trung-tam-duong-lao-hoa-sen-nhat-ban-noi-thay-doi-chu-hieu-co-truyen/20180108075736409\">tour tham quan - tri nghim 24 gi  Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn</a>ngy 6/1, AloBacsi  mi TS.BS Trn Ch Cng, Ch tch Hi Thn kinh v Can thip mch mu no tham gia giao lu v t vn v bnh t qu.</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">ng hn vi chng trnh, ngay sau khi hon tt cc cng vic  TPHCM, TS.BS Trn Ch Cng  chy ln thnh ph mi Bnh Dng  kp chng trnh t vn lc 19g30.</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">Ban u BS Cng cng v l BS.CK2 Phan Trnh Minh Hiu - ngi lun k vai trong cc hot ng  ngha - d tnh n trung tm bng xe ring. Tuy nhin do kt xe lin tc, s tr hn vi cc c ch, nn ng gi hc tr mang xe my ti, mua vi chic nn bo him ca ngi chy xe m ven ng ri t tay chy Honda.</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"justify\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-317 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/BS-Cuong-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" />\r\n<em><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">D thm mt v di chuyn lin tc trong iu kin kt xe, phi chuyn sang xe nh v... tm ng nhng trn tinh thn ht lng v sc khe ca mi ngi, BS Cng vn cp nht kin thc vi phong thi hi hc, d gn nh mi ngy.</span></em></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"justify\">Nhng cu chuyn ca ng khin mi ngi thm mn phc v d ch mi gp nhng  u i gi ng vi ci tn bc s thin thn.</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">D thm mt sau chng ng di nhng BS Cng vn mang n s vui ti cho khn phng vi phong cch tr chuyn gn gi, hm hnh</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n\r\n<strong>1 nm trn th gii mt i mt TPHCM do t qu</strong>\r\n\r\nM u phn t vn, BS Cng cho bit t qu, tim mch v ung th l 3 nguyn nhn gy t vong hng u th gii. Trong , t qu l bnh xy ra t ngt, thi gian tnh bng giy. Nu ung th c th i M, Singapore  cha tr nhng vi t qu th khng. Chnh v vy, ng ni: Chng ta phi t cu ly chng ta.\r\n\r\nNhng con s v t qu m BS Cng a ra nh: 1 nm trn th gii mt i mt TPHCM do t qu, tng ng vi 15 triu ngi, 45 giy c 1 trng hp t qu mi xy ra v trong 3 pht c 1 ca t vong v cn bnh ny khin mi ngi phi git mnh.\r\n\r\nBn cnh khi nim v t qu, phn loi, phng nga, ng cn chia s nhiu kin thc hu ch nh c ti 80% t qu no c du hiu cnh bo trc. V vy, khi c cc du hiu nhn m, yu lit tay chn, kh c ng, ni kh... th cn nhanh chng n bnh vin cp cu.\r\n\r\nVic pht hin v iu tr kp thi rt quan trng, c n 80% c th cu sng ngi bnh. Hin, Vit Nam  c th p dng phng php iu tr t qu mi nht. Trng hp xut huyt no c th can thip ni mch cm mu, loi b d dng mch mu. Trng hp nhi mu no, khi c a n bnh vin thi gian trc 4 gi 30 pht, nu bnh nhn b tc ng mch nh s c bc s bm thuc tan mu ng  ti thng li mch mu b tc, nu n sau thi gian trn n 6 gi hoc tc ng mch ln s c can thip ni mch  ly cc mu ng.\r\n\r\nc ni chuyn vi nhng ngi ln tui nh v vi gia nh, BS Cng chia s thn tnh v c mong trong tng lai c 2 ting chy xe s c mt bnh vin c th thc hin k thut cp cu v x l cc trng hp t qu. y cng l l do m ng thng xuyn i y i   truyn dy kin thc, kinh nghim vi nhiu ng nghip ti cc bnh vin v th h hc tr.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><em><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-318 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/BS-Cuong-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"562\" />\r\nKhch tham gia tour tri nghim 1 ngy  Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn chm ch lng nghe chia s ca TS.BS Trn Ch Cng</em></span></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n\r\nBS Cng hm hnh cho bit, hin cuc sng  ci thin, v th s hiu bit v cc cn bnh ca mi ngi cng c nng cao hn. Tuy nhin, d th no th cng cn phi thm khm v hi  kin ca bc s ch khng th t hnh ng, nht l bnh t qu.\r\n\r\nng dn dt vo iu ny bi trc y  c ngi hi v loi thuc tim lm tan cc mu ng gi trn chc triu c by bn trn th trng. ng nhn mnh, thuc tiu si huyt Actilyse ch c s dng trong bnh vin bi cc bc s chuyn khoa, hn na ch khi bnh nhn b t qu tc mch mu no  c chng minh v loi tr t qu xut huyt no sau khi chp CT. Do , vic iu tr ti nh s khng an ton, thm ch c th gy nguy hi cho bnh nhn.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n\r\n<strong>ng ch quan: Huyt p thp cng c th gy t qu!</strong>\r\n\r\nVi li tr chuyn thu ht, phn chia s ca BS Cng tri qua nhanh chng. ng nh li ban t chc ni, y l c hi qu  c t vn vi chuyn gia giu kinh nghim, rt nhiu cu hi t ra cho v tin s.\r\n\r\nCu hi u tin lin quan n vic V sao ngi cao tui tm bui sng thng hay t qu? BS Cng gii p: Khi ng c th cng ngh ngi, tim rt thng minh nn nhn bit c v ch hot ng 50%. Khi mi ng dy, ngi gi thay i t th t ngt, mu khng kp a ln no  nhn thc nn ko theo 1 chui h lu, trong  c t qu.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"justify\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-319 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/BS-Cuong-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><em>c gp v bc s bc thy v bnh t qu, cc c ch tranh th nh BS Cng gii p thc mc v bnh ny</em></span></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n\r\n tr li cho cu hi Huyt p thp c gy t qu? ngay t u bui tr chuyn, ng  dn dt  mi ngi hiu c nhng nguyn nhn gy ra iu ny ri mi t tn tr li. ng cho bit nhiu ngi tng rng ch tng huyt p mi gy t qu. Tuy nhin, d ch chim kh nng rt thp nhng trong thc t, huyt p thp cng l nguyn nhn dn ti cn bnh nguy him ny do thiu mu ln no. Nu ngi bnh ch quan,  tnh trng huyt p thp ko di th c th dn n t qu.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, vi cu hi t qu c nn chm cu, ct l, ng khuyn co tuyt i khng. Vic cn lm l a bnh nhn n bnh vin trong thi gian vng - 3 gi u  bc s c hng x tr ph hp.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">Hay vi vn  c nhiu ngi quan tm, hi han nhiu nht l Chong u khi lm vic, c cn chp CT?, BS Cng cho hay: Nu bc ch b 1 ln th khng cn thit. Tuy nhin, nu lp li nhiu ln v km theo triu chng khc th nn i khm. Mt s kim tra, xt nghim cn lm l o huyt p, siu m ng mch cnh... T , bc s s c hng x tr. Nu iu tr khng c kt qu th mi chp CT, MRI v cc k thut ny khng nn qu lm dng.</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">Gn cui chng trnh, BS Cng khng qun gii p thm cu hi Suy tnh mch c kh nng gy t qu khng? ca v khch ln tui. ng ni: Suy tnh mch rt thng gp, l tnh trng  tr h thng mch mu, c bit l  2 chn. Bnh thng xy ra  ngi ln tui, lm vic nng nhiu, nhn vin vn phng, hoc mang thai... Bin chng ca bnh ny l s hnh thnh cc cc mu ng trong lng tnh mch. Cc cc mu ny s gy tc mch mu ti ch hoc di chuyn theo dng mu v gy tc mch ch khc, nguy him nht l tc mch phi, t qu....</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">21g, do qung ng xa phi v li TPHCM, BS Cng tic nui hn li vi cc c ch s gii p y  sau khi gi cu hi v cho AloBacsi. Thng v bc s giu nhit huyt, ban t chc  ngh a ng v bng xe hi nhng ng nh nhng t chi bi s anh ti x phi quay li y khuya, cc lm!.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"justify\"><strong>Theo Knh Truyn thng Y t AloBacsi.vn</strong></div>', 'TS.BS Trn Ch Cng tr chuyn thn tnh vi ngi ln tui v bnh t qu', 't qu l cn bnh khng b st bt k i tng no, nht l nhng ngi ln tui khi thi tit thay i t ngt.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ts-bs-tran-chi-cuong-tro-chuyen-than-tinh-voi-nguoi-lon-tuoi-ve-benh-dot-quy', '', '', '2021-01-25 03:44:40', '2021-01-25 03:44:40', '', 0, 'https://g98.com.vn/?p=316', 0, 'post', '', 0),
