cc mu ng gi trn chc triu c by bn trn th trng. ng nhn mnh, thuc tiu si huyt Actilyse ch c s dng trong bnh vin bi cc bc s chuyn khoa, hn na ch khi bnh nhn b t qu tc mch mu no  c chng minh v loi tr t qu xut huyt no sau khi chp CT. Do , vic iu tr ti nh s khng an ton, thm ch c th gy nguy hi cho bnh nhn.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"><strong>ng ch quan: Huyt p thp cng c th gy t qu!</strong>\r\n\r\nVi li tr chuyn thu ht, phn chia s ca BS Cng tri qua nhanh chng. ng nh li ban t chc ni, y l c hi qu  c t vn vi chuyn gia giu kinh nghim, rt nhiu cu hi t ra cho v tin s.\r\n\r\nCu hi u tin lin quan n vic V sao ngi cao tui tm bui sng thng hay t qu? BS Cng gii p: Khi ng c th cng ngh ngi, tim rt thng minh nn nhn bit c v ch hot ng 50%. Khi mi ng dy, ngi gi thay i t th t ngt, mu khng kp a ln no  nhn thc nn ko theo 1 chui h lu, trong  c t qu.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"justify\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-319 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/BS-Cuong-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><em>c gp v bc s bc thy v bnh t qu, cc c ch tranh th nh BS Cng gii p thc mc v bnh ny</em></span></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n<div align=\"justify\"> tr li cho cu hi Huyt p thp c gy t qu? ngay t u bui tr chuyn, ng  dn dt  mi ngi hiu c nhng nguyn nhn gy ra iu ny ri mi t tn tr li. ng cho bit nhiu ngi tng rng ch tng huyt p mi gy t qu. Tuy nhin, d ch chim kh nng rt thp nhng trong thc t, huyt p thp cng l nguyn nhn dn ti cn bnh nguy him ny do thiu mu ln no. Nu ngi bnh ch quan,  tnh trng huyt p thp ko di th c th dn n t qu.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, vi cu hi t qu c nn chm cu, ct l, ng khuyn co tuyt i khng. Vic cn lm l a bnh nhn n bnh vin trong thi gian vng - 3 gi u  bc s c hng x tr ph hp.</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">Hay vi vn  c nhiu ngi quan tm, hi han nhiu nht l Chong u khi lm vic, c cn chp CT?, BS Cng cho hay: Nu bc ch b 1 ln th khng cn thit. Tuy nhin, nu lp li nhiu ln v km theo triu chng khc th nn i khm. Mt s kim tra, xt nghim cn lm l o huyt p, siu m ng mch cnh... T , bc s s c hng x tr. Nu iu tr khng c kt qu th mi chp CT, MRI v cc k thut ny khng nn qu lm dng.</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">Gn cui chng trnh, BS Cng khng qun gii p thm cu hi Suy tnh mch c kh nng gy t qu khng? ca v khch ln tui. ng ni: Suy tnh mch rt thng gp, l tnh trng  tr h thng mch mu, c bit l  2 chn. Bnh thng xy ra  ngi ln tui, lm vic nng nhiu, nhn vin vn phng, hoc mang thai... Bin chng ca bnh ny l s hnh thnh cc cc mu ng trong lng tnh mch. Cc cc mu ny s gy tc mch mu ti ch hoc di chuyn theo dng mu v gy tc mch ch khc, nguy him nht l tc mch phi, t qu....</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\">21g, do qung ng xa phi v li TPHCM, BS Cng tic nui hn li vi cc c ch s gii p y  sau khi gi cu hi v cho AloBacsi. Thng v bc s giu nhit huyt, ban t chc  ngh a ng v bng xe hi nhng ng nh nhng t chi bi s anh ti x phi quay li y khuya, cc lm!.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\" align=\"justify\"><strong>Theo Knh Truyn thng Y t AloBacsi.vn</strong></div>', 'TS.BS Trn Ch Cng tr chuyn thn tnh vi ngi ln tui v bnh t qu', 't qu l cn bnh khng b st bt k i tng no, nht l nhng ngi ln tui khi thi tit thay i t ngt.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '316-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-21 17:30:41', '2021-01-21 17:30:41', '', 316, 'https://g98.com.vn/316-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(321, 1, '2021-01-21 17:36:11', '2021-01-21 17:36:11', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\">B L Th Thanh Hng l i s, cu ni ca nhiu chng trnh, d n Vit - Nht. 30 nm ln ln trn thng trng, i v nh con thoi gia 2 nc, d cch no b cng phi tm c nhng sn phm tt nht t Nht  phn phi cho ngi Vit s dng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-322 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/dsfsdf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"646\" height=\"429\" />\r\n<em><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">B L Th Thanh Hng - Ch tch Hi ng Qun tr kim Tng Gim c Cty TOCONTAP</span></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Khi qua x s mt tri mc, c dp gh thm nhiu vin dng lo, ni no b cng cm nhn c s vui ti, hnh phc v khe mnh. Ngi gi tuy ln tui nhng tm hn li tht tr.  c c iu ny, cc m hnh vin dng lo  Nht c xy dng khoa hc, nhn vn, i ng iu dng l nhng ngi c o to rt bi bn. Cc vin dng lo thm ch cn chm lo c i sng tm linh, tn ngng cho mi ngi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Vy m, khi v n Vit Nam thm hu ht cc vin dng lo b li thy nhng iu ngc li, c s vt cht, trang thit b khng m bo, thiu tnh khoa hc.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Hn na, b hiu rng vi quan nim xa nay ca ngi Vit, sau khi v hu nhiu ngi thng qun mt phi chm sc tui gi, xem vic ng b, cha m chm lo cho con chu l l thng tnh. Thc cht, ngi gi cng c nhng nhu cu c th gin, vui chi, sng v hng th cuc sng theo ng ngha ca n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">T nhng trn tr y, b h quyt tm phi xy dng bng c mt trung tm m   ngi ln tui c th lm nhng iu mnh thch, hng th nhng dch v tt nht, tm t tnh cm c quan tm, chm sc nh ngi thn trong gia nh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Kh khn chng cht, i lc b  mun b cuc nhng mi ln nh n s c n, hiu qunh ca nhng ngi ln tui mnh tng gp b li mm ci, c gng tng cht mt v gi  gp cng hnh thnh nn Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn nh hin ti.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Tt c cc trang thit b u c t mua t cc hng uy tn. B cho bit, \"TOCONTAP chp nhn ct l 10 nm, s c kinh doanh tt cc mng khc  ly cc khon chi khc b vo. Bi chng ti c ao, vin dng lo khng ch l ni n, ng m iu ct li l chm sc ton din sc khe th cht, tinh thn cho ngi ln tui\".</p>', 'V sao Trung tm Hoa Sen chn m hnh chm sc sc khe ngi cao tui ca Nht Bn?', '30% ngi Nht Bn thuc hng cao nin. Tui th trung bnh l 86. H thng Vin dng lo ca Nht c bnh chn ngi nh ng sng nht ca tui x chiu. Trung tm dng lo Hoa Sen, chnh l bn sao hon ho ca Vin Dng lo Nht Bn ti Vit Nam.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vi-sao-trung-tam-hoa-sen-chon-mo-hinh-cham-soc-suc-khoe-nguoi-cao-tuoi-cua-nhat-ban', '', '', '2021-01-28 11:01:24', '2021-01-28 11:01:24', '', 0, 'https://g98.com.vn/?p=321', 0, 'post', '', 0);
