(361, 1, '2021-01-22 06:55:08', '2021-01-22 06:55:08', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-213 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nhan-su-VDL-Hoa-Sen-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1044\" /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\">Gim c: ng Phm Hng Thi</span></p>\r\n<em>C nhn c cu: \"sinh, lo, bnh, t\". Bn giai on ny khng ai c th trnh khi, theo nm thng con ngi ri s gi, v cc chc nng c th s dn dn mt yu i. Mc d vy, nhng cng ln tui th cng tr nn su lng, tinh thn vn sng sut, tri tim vn tip tc hot ng, nhng v c th yu, nn mi hot ng, sinh hot hng ngy tr nn kh khn, cn phi c s tr gip v chm sc.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>V l do , Dng lo Hoa Sen Nht Bn s m nhn vai tr l ngi thn, l thnh vin trong gia nh bng s tn knh v bit n s tn tm chm sc cho nhng bc cao nin, nhng bc cha, ch  to ra x hi ca ngy hm nay.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Vi mong mun p ng nhu cu v sc khe v an dng ca ngi cao tui ti Vit Nam, Chng Ti bng tm huyt ca mnh s to ra mt mi trng ngh dng t tiu chun dnh cho ngi cao tui, mt ni sng m ngi gi cm thy nh sng trong mt gia nh m p, vui v, v tn hng tui gi nh nhng.</em>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-212 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSC04319.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"549\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ec5598;\"><strong>TRIT L KINH DOANHTRUNG TM CHM SC NGI CAO TUI HOA SEN NHT BN</strong></span>\r\n\r\nChng ti, \"Trung tm Hoa Sen Nht Bn\" vi tm nim:\r\n\r\n+ Mang li nim vui v hnh phc cho nhng ngi xung quanh, d  ch l mt vic lm nh.\r\n\r\n+ Phc v tn tm cho Ngi Gi bng c tm lng.\r\n\r\n+ Lun mun cng hin cho x hi bng c tm huyt v lng nhit thnh.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ec5598;\"><strong>PHNG CHM LM VIC</strong></span>\r\n\r\n+ To ra mt khng gian sng thoi mi, vui ti, gn gi.\r\n\r\n+ Mt mi trng lm vic nng ng, ha ng v lun pht trin.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ec5598;\"><strong>PHNG CHM CHM SC NGI CAO TUI</strong></span>\r\n\r\n+ Lun lun knh trng, thng yu. Chm sc tn tm bng c tm lng.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-214 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSC04006b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"625\" /><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\">Qun L: ng Kuragaito Yoshiaki</span></p>\r\n<em>Li u tin, Ti cm n cc bn  quan tm n dch v ca Dng Lo Hoa Sen Nht Bn m hnh Dng Lo cn kh mi i vi Vit Nam, nhng ti Nht Bn, khong 50 nm v trc th t l lo ha  bt u. Khi , Nht Bn ging nh Vit Nam by gi tc  lo ha tng rt nhanh, v tc  lo ha khi  l mt vn  rt ng kinh ngc. Tuy nhin, ngy ny khng phi l tc  lo ha m l s ngi gi v t l lo ha ang tr thnh mt vn  ln trong x hi Nht Bn. Lo ha khng cn l vn  ca mi c nhn, hay gia nh m vn  quan trng l phi cn c s gip  ca x hi.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>T thc t x hi Nht Bn, ti thy Vit Nam trong tng lai s cn rt nhiu nhng vin dng lo, nhng c s chm sc sc khe Ngi CaoTui  p ng cho nhu cu ca x hi. Hin nay, quan nim x hi ngi phng ng ni chung v Vit nam ni ring vic a ng b, cha m n cc vin dng lo l bt hiu nn h vn cn rt r, v rt nhiu ngi cng cha bao gi t t ra cu hi cho bn thn l  Khi gi chng ta s sng  nh hay vo vin dng lo\"? C l cng v l do ny m m hnh kinh doanh vin dng lo vn cha thc s pht trin.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Thc t khi v gi, mc d sng chung vi gia nh, con chu, nhng vi cuc sng ngy nay th gia nh, con chu d mun hay khng cng khng c  thi gian chm sc ng b, cha m mt cch chu o. Trong khi  ti cc c s dng lo s p ng y  cc nhu cu chm sc, ngh dng, vui chi, gii tr.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Vi nhng chia s trn, Ti hy vng mi ngi s c mt ci nhn mi v cch suy ngh tch cc hn v m hnh Dng Lo.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Ti chc mi ngi v gia nh lun lun hnh phc.</em>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ec5598;\"><strong>NHNG TIN CH DNH CHO NGI CAO TUI KHI NGH DNG TI \"HOA SEN NHT BN\"</strong></span>\r\n\r\n* i sng tinh thn thoi mi:\r\n\r\n- Khng gian rng ri, thong mt. Trang thit b hin i\r\n\r\n- Khun vin nhiu cy xanh, khng gian sng gn gi nh gia nh.\r\n\r\n* H tr chm sc 24h/ ngy\r\n\r\nNgi cao tui s cm thy yn tm, bi v vi i ng chuyn gia, iu dng chm sc chuyn nghip h tr chm sc 24h/ ngy.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ec5598;\"><strong>HOT NG TRONG NGY CA NGI CAO TUI TI VIN DNG LO HOA SEN NHT BN</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-210 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Buoi-sang.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"868\" height=\"535\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-211 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Buoi-chieu.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"918\" height=\"539\" />', 'Trung tm Chm sc ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn', 'Trung tm Chm sc ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn mang li nim vui v hnh phc cho nhng ngi xung quanh, d  ch l mt vic lm nh, phc v tn tm cho Ngi Gi bng c tm lng.\r\n\r\n', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '91-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-01-22 06:55:08', '2021-01-22 06:55:08', '', 91, 'https://g98.com.vn/91-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(362, 1, '2021-01-22 07:30:14', '2021-01-22 07:30:14', '<div align=\"justify\">\n\nMt ngy  trung tm dng lo, nhiu ngi ngh  l 24 gi ca mt khng kh hiu ht lm. Nhng mt ngy  trung tm chm sc ngi cao tui ng chun Nht Bn th rt khc.  l ni ngi ln tui hng th 24 gi gm nhng hot ng vui chi thoi mi, tr liu y t, ba n dinh dng ph hp v gic ng ngon trong gian phng thong rng.\n\n l tri nghim ca 19 bn c cao nin tui t 60-84 ca AloBacsi tham dtourtri nghim 1 ngy ti Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn do Cng ty TOCONTAP t chc; AloBacsi tham gia ng t chc vi nhim v tuyn chn khch mi v truyn thng. y l nhng v khch c bit c tham quan trc khi trung tm ct bng khnh thnh n khch.\n\nNgay khi thng tin v chng trnh c ng ti trn AloBacsi, hn 70 ngi  ng k, ho hc c tham d. Tuy nhin, do s lng v  tui gii hn, ban t chc phi hn li nhiu bn c vo chuyn i sau. Cht danh sch 20 khch tham quan, m cui mt bc in thoi xin li v l do ring khng tham d c, bc rt tic v xin kht li ln sau.\n\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-363 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"730\" /><em style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">n vn trang nh, b Hunh Th Hip, ng qun 10, TPHCM c mt t sm, thch th chun b cho chuyn i tri nghim ti trung tm</span></em></p>\n\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">7g30 sng 6/1, xe ca on khch tham quan Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn u tin  ln bnh. Hi hp c l l tm trng chung ca 19 ngi ln tui tham d bi ngay t khi mt tri cha l rng, cc c bc  c mt, sn sng cho chuyn xa nh 24 gi.</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">T hi t nhiu qun khc nhau ca thnh ph v mt v khch c bit n t tnh Qung Ngi, ch sau vi cu cho hi m t xa l  thnh quen bit. Cc c bc chuyn tr rm r sut ng i, n khi bc xung xe  thuc tn nhau nh thn thit t bao gi. C ngi cn chun b sn  n mi bn ng hnh, hay c bc bit Trung tm Hoa Sen Nht Bn rt gn cha B Bnh Dng (mi) nn mang theo ba cy nhang  i ving cha. Ngi gi l vy - hn hu, chu o v cn thn.</span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-364 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" /><em style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn c din tch hn 2.300m2, gm 4 cn nh lin k - mi cn 1 trt 3 lu</span></em></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n\nTrung tm dng lo Hoa Sen Nht Bn n on khch tham quan vi n ci nim n, tc phong chuyn nghip ca cc iu dng v phong cch trang tr tr trung, hin i ca cc gian phng. Nhng chic gh nhiu mu ni bt trn sc trm ca sn g, bn, t... to nn s kt hp hi ha. Sch bo, bn c, bt ch mu, tranh treo tng... c b tr cng rt bt mt.\n\n l cng sc ca i ng chuyn gia n t Nht Bn c kinh nghim xy dng 13 vin dng lo ti Nht.\n\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-365 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" />\n\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-366 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" /><em><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Gng mt ho hng, n ci hi lng n trn mi cc c bc khi c chng kin phong cch chn chu, n cn ca nhng ngi iu dng ln nhn vin qun l</span></em></p>\n\n<div></div>\n</div>\nBc vo mi cn phng t phng ng, nh tm, phng tp th dc, nh bp... mi ngi u chm ch quan st. Cm gic u tin l hi lng v s sch s, thong ng.\n\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n\nBn cnh nhng cu khen ngi, cc c bc cng a ra mt s gp  chn thnh n ban t chc. Mt bc tu to: Phng 7 ngi, tui ngy ln lm, my ngi kia mt ng th sao? Vi tinh thn cu th, ng Phm Hng Thi - Gim c Trung tm Hoa Sen Nht Bn lng nghe, ghi nhn tt c cc gp   \"a ra nhng iu chnh tc thi nhm phc v khch tt nht c th\".\n\nNgoi cc hot ng chm sc sc khe nh tp th dc, vt l tr liu, n huyt xoa bp, trung tm cn ch trng t chc cc chng trnh nng cao tinh thn cho ngi ln tui m bo hai tiu ch: Vui v Khe, chng hn: xp giy, kt ht lm  th cng m ngh, ht karaoke, i do cng vin\n\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-367 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"569\" /></div>\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-368 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"659\" /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khi c hc ngh thut gp giy Nht Bn, cc c bc ho hng tham gia, t m xp ng tng ng nt. Nhng sn phm u tay ny, h s mang v khoe vi con chu  nh.</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\nSau ba tra y  dinh dng gm tm hm rim, tht b xo ci b, canh mp hng nm m... on c gic ng ngn  np nng lng cho cc hot ng bui chiu: tp th dc, ca ht, khiu v Va nhn thy dn karaoke, ng Ng Hin Lng (83 tui) reo ln: Qu ! Nhy m nghen b con!. Ni l lm, chnh cc v khch tc bc hng dn anh ch em iu dng cc bc khiu v vui nhn theo iu nhc.\n<div>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-369 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" />\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-370 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" /></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nhng dng c v ng tc tp th dc  c trung tm nghin cu v thit k dnh ring cho ngi ln tui</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-371 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Vi kinh nghim xy dng 13 vin dng lo  Nht Bn,  trung tm Hoa Sen Nht Bn cc vt dng nh bn n u c thit k theo tiu chun, ph hp vi ngi gi</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<div>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-372 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"879\" height=\"603\" />\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Ba n y  cc cht dinh dng cho chnh tay cc iu dng thc hin. Ti y, khng g b nh cc trung tm khc, nhng ngi ln tui nu c s thch hoc nhu cu cng c th t tay xung ph bp. y khng ch l hot ng gip ch cho th cht ln tinh thn m cn l dp  tr chuyn, chia s v s thch ca ngi ln tui  c s iu chnh thch hp.</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n\nVi s mnh kt ni bc s vi ngi bnh, dp ny AloBacsi cng mi TS.BS Trn Ch Cng - Ch tch Hi can thip Thn kinh t qu TPHCM n<a href=\"https://alobacsi.com/dot-quy/ts-bs-tran-chi-cuong-tro-chuyen-than-tinh-voi-nguoi-lon-tuoi-ve-benh-dot-quy/20180108073328305\">tr chuyn v bnh t qu</a>v BS.CK1 Trnh Ngc Bnh t vn, thm khm cho 19 thnh vin.\n\nVi cu hi v sao ngi cao tui tm bui sng thng hay t qu? BS Cng tr li: Khi ng c th cng ngh ngi, tim rt thng minh nn nhn bit c v ch hot ng 50%. Khi mi ng dy, ngi gi thay i t th t ngt, mu khng kp a ln no  kp nhn thc nn ko theo mt chui h lu... trong  c t qu.\n\nMt bc hi t qu c nn chm cu, ct l v tin s nhn mnh: Bnh nhn nn n bnh vin trong thi gian vng (3 gi u)  bc s c hng x tr ph hp, hn ch ti thiu di chng.\n\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-373 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Phn giao lu ca TS.BS Trn Ch Cng nhn c s quan tm ca cc v khch tham gia tour tri nghim 1 ngy  Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn</span></div>\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n\nTip ni chng trnh, cc thnh vin ca on c BS.CK1 Trnh Ngc Bnh - ngi c nhiu nm cng tc ti khoa Cp cu BV Ch Ry, Ph phng truyn thng, chuyn gia t vn ca AloBacsi - thm khm, nh vy, mt thnh vin trong on b tng huyt p c dng thuc kp thi. Cc c bc khc th bit cch chm sc cc bnh mn tnh khc ca mnh.\n\nNgy u tin ca chuyn tham quan kt thc vi gic ng ngon trn nhng chic ging hin i v tin nghi, c nhp khu t Nht Bn.\n\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-374 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"506\" /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ngy tip theo, c on n bnh minh ti cng vin gn , vi nhng bi tp b ch do ng Kuragaito Yoshiaki - qun l ca trung tm hng dn</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div align=\"justify\">Bnh minh ngy 7/1 va ln, ng Kuragaito Yoshiaki - qun l ca trung tm  mi mi ngi thc gic v hng dn nhng bi tp nh nhng nh xoay cc khp tay, vn mnh... Bu tri trong xanh, gi nh sau mt m ngon gic lm tm trng tr nn nh nhng, th thi.</div>\n<div align=\"justify\"></div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<div align=\"center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-375 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"692\" /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Sau li cm n chn thnh, ng Phm Hng Thi - Gim c Trung tm Hoa Sen Nht Bn trao tng qu cho khch tham quan</span></div>\n<div align=\"center\"></div>\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">Sau ba sng l t cho g nng hi, cc c ch cng nhau chp hnh lu nim v nhn phn qu l nm m Yoshimoto c trng trn cao nguyn Bo Lc, bt rau xanh Nht Bn... t ban t chc trao tn tay cc c ch. Mn qu nh nhng cha ng tm lng rt ln, bi tt c u sn xut theo ng tiu chun Nht, m bo tt cho sc khe.</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-376 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">ng Kuragaito Yoshiaki mang m phong cch ca ngi Nht, t ci ci cho, bt tay, tr chuyn u tot ln s trn trng vi bc cao nin. Khi xe ln bnh ri i, ng khng qun ci cho, vy tay tm bit n khi xe khut hn. S tip i thn tnh nh ngi trong gia nh, ng nhn c nhiu li khen t khch tham d, no l p trai, d mn, gn gi v rt t m trong tng chi tit</span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-377 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-15.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trc khi xe ln bnh v TPHCM, c on chp hnh lu nim cng qun l v iu dng ca trung tm</span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\nGi chia tay  im, 1 ngy tri qua tht nhanh. Mi hm qua cha ai bit nhau, vy m ch sau 24 gi nh  thn thit t lu. iu ng li trong tim mi ngi khng ch l mt ngy c chm sc, vui chi m cn  nhng cm xc l tnh thn, tnh bn m khng phi lc no cng c th cm nhn c.\n\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n\nCc c bc h hi: V y vui gh, ch  nh con ci i lm sut, bun lm. Cng u c d m ngy no cng i thm bn b!, ri h hn nhau: ng nh v (vin dng lo) thng my? Tui vi ng cng v cng lc cho vui!\n\nNhc n vin dng lo, nhiu ngi ngh n ni c n ca ngi gi khi khng c con ci bn cnh... Giao ph vic chm sc cha m cho ngi khc b xem l bt hiu trong quan nim lu i ca ngi Vit Nam. Th nhng, vi m hnh hin i, m p - ni ngi cao tui tht s c ngh ngi, sng nhng ngy vui khe ch khng phi tip ni chui ht lo cho con li chm cho chu, th a cha m vo trung tm dng lo mi tht s l ch hiu.\n\n</div>\n<div align=\"justify\">\n<div>\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-378 size-full\" src=\"https://g98.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Hoa-Sen-Nhat-Ban-16.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"621\" />\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Chuyn thm trung tm ln ny cn c s tham d c bit ca b L Th Thanh Hng (th 5 t tri qua) - Ch tch Hi ng Qun tr kim Tng Gim c Cty TOCONTAP. Vi kinh nghim hn 30 nm lm vic vi hng trm i tc Nht Bn, c chng kin m hnh vin dng lo ng chun  nc bn, b khng thi trn tr v mt ni c th chm sc ngi gi hin i nhng vn m m nh nhng ngi thn trong gia nh. B mun vit nn mt tp truyn di v chng ng chm sc ngi cao tui v s tri nghim ln ny ca 19 c ch chnh l lt trang u tin ca cu chuyn.</span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Trung tm dng lo Hoa Sen Nht Bn - ni thay i ch Hiu c truyn', 'Xa nay, nhiu ngi quan nim a cha m vo vin dng lo l bt hiu. Th nhng, vi m hnh v phong cch ca Trung tm chm sc Ngi cao tui Hoa Sen Nht Bn, quan nim v ch Hiu dn thay i.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '182-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-01-22 07:30:14', '2021-01-22 07:30:14', '', 182, 'https://g98.com.vn/182-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
